# Required Environment Variables for OTP System

## Add these to your .env file:

# Resend API Key (for sending OTP emails)
RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Supabase Service Role Key (for session management)
# ⚠️ CRITICAL: Keep this secret! Never expose client-side.
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

## How to get these keys:

### RESEND_API_KEY
1. Go to https://resend.com
2. Sign up or log in
3. Navigate to "API Keys" in dashboard
4. Create a new API key
5. Copy and paste it above

### SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
1. Go to your Supabase project dashboard
2. Navigate to "Settings" → "API"
3. Find "service_role" key under "Project API keys"
4. Copy the key (it starts with "eyJ...")
5. Paste it above

⚠️ The service_role key has full database access - treat it like a password!

## Email Configuration

Don't forget to update the sender email in:
/app/api/auth/send-otp/route.ts

Change this line:
```typescript
from: 'Car Dashboard <noreply@yourdomain.com>',
```

To your verified Resend domain email address.
